OL,3,CPolice apologise to family of dead
OL,4,CSomerset mother for 'unacceptable'
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FAvon and Somerset Police have
OL,8,Fapologised to the family of Kelly
OL,9,FFaiers after the police watchdog said
OL,10,Ftheir decision not to arrest her sex
OL,11,Foffender partner on the day she died
OL,12,Fwas "unacceptable".
OL,14,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC) said the force "could
OL,16,Fand should have done better" in the
OL,17,Fwake of Kelly Faiers' death following
OL,18,Fan investigation.
