OL,3,CPolice apologise to family of dead
OL,4,CSomerset mother for 'unacceptable'
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FThe 61-year-old died at the home of
OL,8,FRichard Scatchard, 70, in Minehead in
OL,9,FOctober 2023.
OL,11,FPolice spoke to Mr Scatchard, a
OL,12,Fconvicted sex offender, on the day she
OL,13,Fdied but chose not to arrest him
OL,14,Fdespite "concerns" about his
OL,15,Fbehaviour, the IOPC said.
OL,17,FHe disappeared the next day, prompting
OL,18,Fa six-month manhunt which ended when
OL,19,Fhis body was found in a caravan in
OL,20,FApril 2024.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
