OL,3,CPolice apologise to family of dead
OL,4,CSomerset mother for 'unacceptable'
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,FA spokesman for the force said: "We
OL,8,Fwould like to apologise to Kelly
OL,9,FFaiers' family for the impact of
OL,10,Fseveral of the decisions made by Avon
OL,11,Fand Somerset Police during the course
OL,12,Fof our enquiries into her death.
OL,14,F"Ms Faiers' death in Minehead on 15
OL,15,FOctober 2023 was initially considered
OL,16,Fto be non-suspicious.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
