OL,3,CPolice apologise to family of dead
OL,4,CSomerset mother for 'unacceptable'
OL,5,Cfailures
OL,7,F"An operational decision was made the
OL,8,Ffollowing day to then treat Ms Faiers'
OL,9,Fdeath at Richard Scatchard's home as
OL,10,Fsuspicious and that it should be
OL,11,Finvestigated as a murder inquiry.
OL,13,F"This update was not relayed to the
OL,14,Ffamily for a further 48 hours, in part
OL,15,Fdue to being unable to locate trained
OL,16,Ffamily liaison officers to meet Ms
OL,17,FFaiers' family and deliver the update
OL,18,Fin-person.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
