OL,7,FAvon and Somerset Police added they
OL,8,Fconsider it "inappropriate" to comment
OL,9,Ffurther on their decision not to
OL,10,Farrest Mr Scatchard at the scene of Ms
OL,11,FFaiers' death due to ongoing
OL,12,Fproceedings by the coroner.
OL,14,FCCTV footage shows Ms Faiers and Mr
OL,15,FScatchard together in Minehead on the
OL,16,Fevening of her death
